Project Setup Checklist:

    Clone the Repository:

    Clone the repo using git clone <repo-url>

Install Dependencies:

    Run npm install in the project directory to install all required packages.

Set Up .env File:

    Create a .env file in the root directory with the following entries:

        MONGO_URI=<your-mongo-db-connection-url>

        SECRET_KEY=<your-jwt-secret-key>

Start the Server:

    Run npm start to start the server locally.

